
Taken from McCalls, March 2001 issue:

Heinous Husband Award
One night after I'd asked my husband, Keith, to bring our cat inside, he 
reported that she hissed at him.  The next morning I found out why she'd been 
hostile.  It wasn't our cat!  After Keith got home from work, I introduced 
him to Brandy--whom we've had for five years."